database.py

Purpose:
This file is used to create the connection between FastAPI and MySQL database. It contains database username, password, database name, and manages database sessions.

---

models.py

Purpose:
This file is used to convert MySQL tables into Python classes. It defines the structure of database tables for FastAPI.

---

schemas.py

Purpose:
This file is used to define the API request and response format. It controls how data is sent and received.

---

main.py

Purpose:
This is the main file of the FastAPI application. It starts the application and connects all API routes together.
